query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char, MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress, MIN(t.title) AS voiced_animation FROM aka_name AS an, complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, company_name AS cn, info_type AS it, info_type AS it3, keyword AS k, movie_companies AS mc, movie_info AS mi, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, person_info AS pi, role_type AS rt, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND cn.id = mc.company_id AND it.id = mi.info_type_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND rt.id = ci.role_id AND n.id = an.person_id AND ci.person_id = an.person_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = pi.person_id AND ci.person_id = pi.person_id AND it3.id = pi.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it3.info not in ('languages','LD dialogue intellegibility','LD laserdisc title','weekend gross','biographical movies','salary history','top 250 rank','LD language','LD analog left','nick names','LD supplement','LD close captions-teletext-ld-g','LD release country','LD contrast','birth date') AND it.info in ('agent address','birth date','LD laserdisc title','crazy credits','salary history','plot','LD number of sides','LD analog left','where now','copyright holder','death date','color info','LD release date') AND (rt.role like '%Emily Weber%' OR rt.role like '%Rod Glenn%' OR rt.role like '%BEF%' OR rt.role like '%alpowell%') AND mi.info in ('Afrikaans','Gujarati','Greek','Cantonese','German','Persian','Russian','Turkish','Inuktitut','Ukrainian','Norwegian','Serbo-Croatian') AND (an.name like '%w%' OR an.name like '%G%') AND cct2.kind in ('cast','complete','crew') AND (k.keyword like '%dream%' OR k.keyword like '%danger%') AND (pi.note like '%Eldorado%') AND chn.name not like '%Ellen Ripley%' AND chn.name not like '%Willy Wonka%' AND chn.name not like '%Rambo%' AND chn.name not like '%Tony Stark%' AND chn.name not like '%Donnie Darko%'
